room_title: Escape room "C.S.I." by Escape Frenzy in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: Our family escaped the CSI room with 46 seconds left! It was so much fun! The staff was so awesome as well.

room_title: Escape room "C.S.I." by Escape Frenzy in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: What an enjoyable evening we all had! With seconds to spare, we solved the C.S.I. mystery. It's not easy, but it is a lot of fun.

room_title: Escape room "C.S.I." by Escape Frenzy in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: We escaped from the CSI room. Really fun and challenging. Already talking about coming back to try another one. Thanks for the great evening.

room_title: Escape room "C.S.I." by Escape Frenzy in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: Our family did the CSI room and all 5 of us had a blast! We broke out with 3 minutes to spare, as we stepped out of the room my 16-year-old was ready to try another room! We'll definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "C.S.I." by Escape Frenzy in Minneapolis - St. Paul
review: Loved this place! Went as a family of 4 and was lucky enough to be just us in the Crime Scene room. It was awesome. Son (15) and daughter (11) were in heaven as we battled time to understand the clues. Made it out with about 1:30 seconds left in our hour. Will definitely try some other rooms and may be back as a team building exercise. Our hearts were pounding the entire drive home!
